                   'M8' => '“If people are doubting how far you can go, go so far that you can’t hear them anymore.” – Michele Ruiz',
                   'M9' => '“We need to accept that we won’t always make the right decisions, that we’ll screw up royally sometimes – understanding that failure is not the opposite of success, it’s part of success.” – Arianna Huffington',
                   'M10' => '“Write it. Shoot it. Publish it. Crochet it, sauté it, whatever. MAKE.” – Joss Whedon',
