                   'M12' => '“Everything you can imagine is real.”― Pablo Picasso',
                   'M13' => '“When one door of happiness closes, another opens; but often we look so long at the closed door that we do not see the one which has been opened for us.” ― Helen Keller',
                   'M14' => '“Do one thing every day that scares you.”― Eleanor Roosevelt',
                   'M15' => '“It’s no use going back to yesterday, because I was a different person then.”― Lewis Carroll',
                   'M16' => '“Smart people learn from everything and everyone, average people from their experiences, stupid people already have all the answers.” – Socrates',
