                   'M18' => '“Whatever you are, be a good one.” ― Abraham Lincoln',
                   'M19' => '“Impossible is just an opinion.” – Paulo Coelho',
                   'M20' => '“You can either experience the pain of discipline or the pain of regret. The choice is yours.”  – Unknown',
                   'M21' => '“If we have the attitude that it’s going to be a great day it usually is.” – Catherine Pulsifier',
